title: Vivaramana Aalu
subTitle: A robber abandons his wife for a wealthy woman, but soon regrets his decision. Later, he returns, vowing to win back her trust and prove his love.

title: Varusham 16
subTitle: Kannan, a teenager, falls in love with his uncle's daughter, Radhika, but things turn upside down when her grandmother disapproves of their relationship.

title: Ayiram Janmangal
subTitle: Ravi is happily married to Savitri and they go to his estate for a vacation with her brother. There, Savitri gets possessed by the ghost of Radha, Ravi's previous lover.

title: Rajadurai
subTitle: Rajadurai, a police officer, succeeds in capturing Mayandi, a gangster, and sending him to jail. Later, Mayandi kidnaps Rajadurai's son, Vijay, and raises him as a criminal.

title: Vithagan
subTitle: Rowdhiran, a tough and honest cop, seeks revenge on a criminal gang. However, when Badri, the mob boss, plots his downfall, Rowdhiran decides to go down swinging.

title: Rajadhi Raja
subTitle: Raja, a rich estate owner's son, comes back from abroad in order to avenge his dead father. However, things get complicated when he is framed, and he finds his doppelganger in his village.

title: Vandhaan Vendraan
subTitle: On the request of the woman he loves, Arjun goes to great lengths to put his half-brother Ramana, who is a don, behind bars. However, his attempts put him in a dangerous situation.

title: Villadhi Villain
